WEBVTT

1
00:03:36.591 --> 00:03:38.134
You'd be giving up your dream.

2
00:03:38.218 --> 00:03:44.682
Yeah. Honestly.
when I thought I was pregnant.

3
00:03:44.766 --> 00:03:47.143
I was scared at first.

4
00:03:47.227 --> 00:03:50.939
But when you told me
my career would be over.

5
00:03:51.022 --> 00:03:56.110
it was odd. but suddenly. I felt relieved.

6
00:03:56.861 --> 00:04:03.409
I don't have any privacy.
and always having to be perfect…

7
00:04:03.493 --> 00:04:07.038
it's too hard.

8
00:04:07.121 --> 00:04:09.958
Once I tell my dad.
you know there's no going back.

9
00:04:11.334 --> 00:04:12.585
I know.

10
00:04:12.669 --> 00:04:15.797
But fame isn't what I want.

11
00:04:18.174 --> 00:04:23.471
Min Ho. I'm really sorry.
I didn't know it would turn out like this.

12
00:04:24.472 --> 00:04:26.391
No. you should do what you want.

13
00:04:27.392 --> 00:04:29.018
Thank you so much.

14
00:06:24.926 --> 00:06:27.178
Oh yes. Yes.

15
00:06:27.261 --> 00:06:30.640
Truthfully. this reservation is
for the designer Yisoo--

16
00:06:30.723 --> 00:06:31.808
Hello?

17
00:10:51.275 --> 00:10:55.154
- What would you like to eat?
- One kimchi dumpling.

18
00:10:55.237 --> 00:10:56.489
One <i>pajeon…</i>

19
00:10:59.241 --> 00:11:02.328
And three <i>yukhwae bibimbaps</i>
as well. please.

20
00:11:02.411 --> 00:11:04.789
Oh no. Can you take off
one <i>yukhwae. </i>please?

21
00:11:04.872 --> 00:11:07.291
- So two <i>yukhwae bibimbaps?</i>
- Yes. please. Thank you.

22
00:19:24.746 --> 00:19:26.290
Hey. what are you doing?

23
00:19:26.790 --> 00:19:29.168
I just got an email from Seoul National.

24
00:19:30.544 --> 00:19:31.712
I didn't get in.

25
00:19:33.714 --> 00:19:36.258
Really? You're the first in our class.

26
00:19:39.178 --> 00:19:43.640
I was always worried I wouldn't be
able to go because of the money.

27
00:19:45.642 --> 00:19:48.645
I never even thought I wouldn't get in.

28
00:19:51.899 --> 00:19:56.069
Yuri asked me the other day
if I had my own dream.

29
00:19:58.030 --> 00:19:59.656
Dream? You have one?

30
00:20:01.408 --> 00:20:02.618
I do.

31
00:20:04.077 --> 00:20:05.329
But it's a little crazy.

32
00:20:05.412 --> 00:20:06.788
Is it music. by chance?

33
00:20:07.664 --> 00:20:09.374
How did you know?

34
00:20:09.458 --> 00:20:11.919
Last year you held yourself back
from the stage.

35
00:20:12.002 --> 00:20:13.587
but you ended up doing really well.

36
00:20:15.631 --> 00:20:17.049
I have an idea…

37
00:20:20.052 --> 00:20:23.513
Wouldn't it be fun
if you and I made music together?

38
00:20:23.597 --> 00:20:26.558
It would be fun. of course.
but is that as easy as it sounds?

39
00:20:26.642 --> 00:20:29.478
It won't be easy.
but it's something you have a taste for.

40
00:20:29.561 --> 00:20:31.480
What do you say?
